WEBVTT

01:27.390 --> 01:31.830
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.180 --> 01:34.920
[Episode 9]

01:36.789 --> 01:38.390
This topic is very valuable.

01:39.640 --> 01:41.100
How did you come up with it?

01:41.479 --> 01:42.759
Before, when we were at the beach,

01:42.759 --> 01:44.400
you asked me to write something,

01:44.400 --> 01:45.590
and I started wondering

01:45.590 --> 01:48.720
where those characters
were eventually carried off to.

01:50.550 --> 01:51.340
Look.

01:53.280 --> 01:54.789
In the second section here,

01:54.789 --> 01:56.670
you should first provide

01:56.920 --> 01:58.520
a summary of the wave theory.

01:59.000 --> 02:01.310
For example, the randomness of waves,

02:01.680 --> 02:03.560
the theory of
small-amplitude wave fluctuations,

02:03.560 --> 02:06.200
numerical simulation methods
for waves, and so on.

02:06.200 --> 02:07.500
From this foundation,

02:07.840 --> 02:09.430
you can then move into your own argument.

02:09.430 --> 02:09.979
Okay.

02:10.430 --> 02:12.000
I'll go back and think it over.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.930
I'll show you once I've revised it.

02:14.800 --> 02:15.150
Keep it up.

02:15.150 --> 02:16.210
Thank you, Ms. Yan.

02:17.240 --> 02:17.800
Director Lin.

02:17.800 --> 02:19.000
Hello, Director Lin.

02:20.079 --> 02:21.800
I heard you've been working
really hard recently,

02:21.800 --> 02:23.730
spending every day in the library.

02:24.960 --> 02:27.079
Her paper outline is well written.

02:27.240 --> 02:28.560
If she puts in the effort,

02:28.560 --> 02:30.360
it should turn out to be
a pretty valuable paper.

02:30.360 --> 02:30.820
Not bad.

02:30.910 --> 02:31.510
Well done.

02:31.870 --> 02:33.130
Hurry up and finish it,

02:33.310 --> 02:35.079
so you can graduate with everyone else.

02:35.079 --> 02:35.410
Okay.

02:35.710 --> 02:36.710
Thank you, Director Lin.

02:36.710 --> 02:37.430
Thank you, Ms. Yan.

02:37.430 --> 02:38.760
I'll take my leave then.

02:43.079 --> 02:44.120
I hope this child

02:44.750 --> 02:46.150
is worthy of your help.

02:47.400 --> 02:50.200
Well, this is just
what a teacher should do, right?

02:52.910 --> 02:54.010
Please sit, Director.

02:54.010 --> 02:54.670
You sit too.

02:58.360 --> 02:58.910
Here's the thing,

02:58.910 --> 02:59.430
Ms. Yan.

02:59.910 --> 03:01.010
Next month,

03:01.430 --> 03:03.960
there's going to be a scholarship
donation program in our school.

03:03.960 --> 03:06.080
The administration is currently
coordinating it.

03:06.080 --> 03:08.280
But considering relevance to majors—

03:08.680 --> 03:10.840
especially that
our Oceanography Department

03:10.840 --> 03:11.870
has made outstanding achievements

03:11.870 --> 03:12.930
in talent training

03:12.960 --> 03:14.240
and discipline development

03:14.240 --> 03:15.120
over the years—

03:15.840 --> 03:17.000
the scholarship

03:17.000 --> 03:19.800
will be somewhat prioritized
for our department.

03:21.120 --> 03:24.160
A scholarship is a good thing
for the students.

03:25.400 --> 03:27.000
This is a long-term project,

03:27.030 --> 03:29.360
and on behalf of the department,
we want to

03:29.560 --> 03:31.290
assign you to take charge of it.

03:31.520 --> 03:32.000
Me?

03:33.079 --> 03:33.800
Ms. Yan.

03:34.520 --> 03:35.360
The school

03:35.800 --> 03:36.400
knows that

03:36.750 --> 03:38.400
what happened with Li Changning

03:38.400 --> 03:39.680
caused you some unfair treatment

03:39.680 --> 03:42.680
and affected this year's
professional title evaluation.

03:42.680 --> 03:44.000
Your overall ability is strong,

03:44.000 --> 03:45.520
and you care about the students—

03:45.520 --> 03:46.780
this is evident to all.

03:47.190 --> 03:48.630
In next year's evaluation,

03:48.630 --> 03:50.360
there will definitely be no problem.

03:50.360 --> 03:51.400
We certainly don't want to miss out

03:51.400 --> 03:52.530
on a talent like you.

03:54.120 --> 03:55.190
So you mean

03:55.840 --> 03:57.500
I can be reappointed as usual?

03:57.550 --> 03:57.860
Yes.

03:58.400 --> 03:59.800
Here, take a look at this.

04:02.560 --> 04:03.000
The other party

04:03.000 --> 04:04.860
is a maritime logistics company.

04:04.870 --> 04:06.660
If the talk goes well,

04:07.190 --> 04:08.560
besides the scholarship,

04:08.560 --> 04:09.290
we might even

04:09.680 --> 04:11.080
be able to help secure jobs

04:11.080 --> 04:12.540
for some of our graduates.

04:14.870 --> 04:15.400
I have to say,

04:15.400 --> 04:16.180
that Mr. Ding

04:16.269 --> 04:17.399
has quite a good eye.

04:17.550 --> 04:18.610
[Project Information]

04:17.680 --> 04:20.470
He said he met you at an academic seminar

04:18.630 --> 04:20.329
[Project Name:
Xinghan Scholarship Donation Program]

04:20.500 --> 04:21.720
and had a very good impression of you.

04:21.720 --> 04:22.630
He even specifically proposed

04:22.630 --> 04:24.040
that you serve as

04:24.040 --> 04:26.360
a member of
this scholarship review committee.

04:24.260 --> 04:25.260
[Donor: Oceanvision International Group]

04:25.270 --> 04:26.610
[Recipient:
Li Hai University of Science and Technology]

04:26.650 --> 04:30.440
[Lihai Mingde International Hospital]

04:28.510 --> 04:30.170
What's this supposed to mean?

04:30.720 --> 04:31.850
Even if I lose my job,

04:32.680 --> 04:34.940
I wouldn't accept any handouts from you.

04:35.680 --> 04:37.010
I'm really speechless.

04:38.390 --> 04:39.870
It's only you and your mom

04:40.240 --> 04:41.500
that I can't get mad at.

04:42.120 --> 04:43.120
If it were anyone else,

04:43.120 --> 04:43.920
go ask around—

04:44.480 --> 04:46.409
who would dare talk to me like that?

04:50.630 --> 04:52.390
Your mom called to beg me.

04:53.070 --> 04:54.950
Seeing the genuine sincerity in her,

04:54.950 --> 04:56.190
I really felt for her.

04:57.140 --> 04:57.920
I didn't expect that

04:57.920 --> 05:00.120
my good intentions totally backfired.

05:00.920 --> 05:03.360
What was the point of me
spending that 10 million then—

05:03.360 --> 05:05.690
just so you could
take your anger out on me?

05:06.240 --> 05:07.900
You said my mom came to beg you?

05:08.070 --> 05:08.730
What else?

05:09.270 --> 05:11.730
Your mom said
you were going to lose your job.

05:13.870 --> 05:15.560
Why did you do this?

05:16.950 --> 05:19.600
Why did you call him
to talk about my situation?

05:20.920 --> 05:22.650
Why are you losing your temper?

05:22.920 --> 05:24.190
Your Uncle Ding called and said

05:24.190 --> 05:26.320
that your job issue has been resolved.

05:26.920 --> 05:29.520
I don't need him to
resolve my job issues for me.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.430
Didn't I tell you

05:33.480 --> 05:36.070
that the school didn't say
they wanted me to leave?

05:36.070 --> 05:37.600
From now on, if you have any thoughts

05:37.600 --> 05:38.680
about my matters,

05:39.120 --> 05:41.460
can you come and talk to me directly?

05:41.490 --> 05:42.890
What should I talk to you?

05:43.800 --> 05:44.860
You are already 36,

05:45.060 --> 05:47.630
just like me, spending half your life
as a struggling teacher,

05:47.630 --> 05:49.630
and you even have a child to support.

05:49.870 --> 05:51.730
If the school were to kick you out,

05:51.800 --> 05:52.860
who would hire you?

05:53.700 --> 05:55.070
You're unwilling to ask for help,

05:55.070 --> 05:57.120
so I swallowed my pride to plead for you.

05:57.120 --> 05:58.450
Did I do anything wrong?

06:00.240 --> 06:02.870
But you didn't consider my feelings, Mom.

06:05.390 --> 06:07.390
He donated 10 million to the school.

06:09.520 --> 06:11.630
He donated 10 million for your sake?

06:12.240 --> 06:14.770
Our family couldn't repay it
in generations.

06:15.600 --> 06:18.360
Your Uncle Ding is truly
loyal and affectionate.

06:18.430 --> 06:20.430
He treats you like his own daughter.

06:30.800 --> 06:32.270
So I have to owe him for a lifetime,

06:32.270 --> 06:32.830
right?

06:34.950 --> 06:35.980
Whatever he says,

06:36.390 --> 06:37.480
I have to listen to him.

06:37.480 --> 06:38.409
Is that how it is?

06:39.040 --> 06:40.170
How can you say that?

06:40.230 --> 06:42.040
You really don't know what's good for you!

06:42.040 --> 06:42.950
Even though he's so ill,

06:42.950 --> 06:44.159
he still cares about your matters.

06:44.159 --> 06:45.000
It's only right

06:45.000 --> 06:46.720
if you honor him

06:46.870 --> 06:48.270
like an elder in the family.

06:48.270 --> 06:50.400
Back then, you caused your dad's death

06:50.720 --> 06:52.390
when he came back to visit.

06:52.480 --> 06:54.190
It didn't even count as a work injury.

06:54.190 --> 06:55.360
In the end, it was your Uncle Ding

06:55.360 --> 06:57.570
who helped us secure the compensation.

06:58.040 --> 06:59.680
And after your high school entrance exam,

06:59.680 --> 07:01.680
wasn't it your Uncle Ding who ran around

07:01.680 --> 07:02.610
pulling strings

07:02.630 --> 07:03.430
to get you into

07:03.430 --> 07:05.230
the provincial key high school?

07:06.070 --> 07:07.930
You should be grateful, Yan Ling.

07:09.920 --> 07:11.680
It's true that you did quite well,

07:11.680 --> 07:14.830
but at most, that would have gotten you
into a key school in our city.

07:14.830 --> 07:17.190
But Uncle Ding got you into

07:17.190 --> 07:18.560
a provincial key school.

07:18.560 --> 07:20.050
That took a lot of effort.

07:21.360 --> 07:23.360
Uncle Ding's kindness to our family

07:23.370 --> 07:26.030
is something we could never repay
in a lifetime.

07:26.830 --> 07:28.520
We have to show gratitude.

07:48.720 --> 07:49.310
Miss!

07:49.750 --> 07:51.950
Your phone has been ringing for a while.

08:02.950 --> 08:05.390
Ms. Yan, I saw him again.

08:08.870 --> 08:09.960
Changning!

08:11.040 --> 08:12.450
Li Changning!

08:16.800 --> 08:19.080
Don't do anything stupid, Changning!

08:19.190 --> 08:20.520
Li Changning!

08:26.510 --> 08:27.390
Li Changning!

08:27.390 --> 08:28.430
Get back here!

08:32.080 --> 08:32.880
Get back here!

08:33.480 --> 08:34.960
Get back here! Come back with me!

08:34.960 --> 08:36.240
Get back here! Come back with me!

08:36.240 --> 08:37.390
I'm not trying to kill myself,

08:37.390 --> 08:37.980
Ms. Yan!

08:38.120 --> 08:39.490
I'm not trying to kill myself!

08:39.490 --> 08:41.000
I just want to wash away

08:41.000 --> 08:43.630
the shameful and stupid things
he left on me!

08:44.630 --> 08:45.660
-Wash them all away!
-Changning!

08:45.660 --> 08:46.640
Wash them away!

08:51.440 --> 08:52.100
Changning!

08:52.150 --> 08:53.470
Come back with me!

08:54.430 --> 08:55.380
So close.

08:56.350 --> 08:57.790
How could you bring her here?

08:57.790 --> 08:59.360
You said this place belongs to us—

08:59.360 --> 09:00.200
just the two of us!

09:00.200 --> 09:00.670
What are you doing?

09:00.670 --> 09:01.030
Stop it.

09:01.030 --> 09:02.200
I broke up with you a long time ago.

09:02.200 --> 09:03.800
I do want to break up with you!

09:04.360 --> 09:05.270
I came here just to

09:05.270 --> 09:07.070
make a clean break with the past.

09:07.120 --> 09:08.530
But how could you...

09:09.270 --> 09:10.200
How could you...

09:11.390 --> 09:12.210
I thought

09:12.440 --> 09:14.200
when a relationship ends

09:14.220 --> 09:15.120
and fades away,

09:15.340 --> 09:17.610
at least the good parts would remain.

09:18.180 --> 09:20.530
But he denied everything between us—

09:20.600 --> 09:22.270
he denied our past,

09:22.360 --> 09:23.960
and he completely denied me!

09:24.030 --> 09:25.630
Your stupidity disgusts me!

09:26.350 --> 09:27.120
What makes you

09:27.120 --> 09:28.320
think you deserve me?

09:29.560 --> 09:30.960
Just because you slept with me?

09:30.960 --> 09:31.960
Country bumpkin.

09:32.000 --> 09:33.790
Look at yourself, you hillbilly.

09:33.790 --> 09:35.610
What right do you have to talk to me
about love?

09:35.610 --> 09:36.670
It's not like that.

09:36.740 --> 09:37.550
It's not like that.

09:37.550 --> 09:38.270
It is!

09:38.270 --> 09:39.390
It just is!

09:40.140 --> 09:40.970
Changning!

09:41.630 --> 09:42.290
Changning!

09:43.720 --> 09:44.390
Changning!

09:44.390 --> 09:46.230
He bullied me and humiliated me

09:46.480 --> 09:47.410
again and again.

09:47.710 --> 09:48.830
Yes, yes—

09:49.610 --> 09:51.220
I am indeed heartbroken,

09:51.390 --> 09:53.600
but that's because
I finally saw clearly that

09:53.600 --> 09:56.060
what I fell in love with
wasn't even a person!

09:56.080 --> 09:57.480
He's a devil.

09:57.510 --> 09:58.670
He's a beast!

10:01.510 --> 10:02.320
Ms. Yan.

10:03.150 --> 10:04.750
I heard from the school

10:05.000 --> 10:06.870
that you took the disciplinary action
in my place.

10:06.870 --> 10:08.130
You saved me.

10:08.840 --> 10:10.990
A large part of the new me

10:11.360 --> 10:12.600
is because of you.

10:13.720 --> 10:15.000
I will absolutely never

10:15.000 --> 10:17.670
let that beast break me again!

10:18.600 --> 10:19.420
You said

10:19.510 --> 10:21.320
that everything will get better,

10:21.320 --> 10:22.840
that everything will pass,

10:22.840 --> 10:24.700
and I'll live well and keep going,

10:24.960 --> 10:25.840
right?

10:26.750 --> 10:27.360
Right?

10:31.000 --> 10:32.400
Everything will be fine.

10:32.890 --> 10:34.490
Everything will get better.

10:35.600 --> 10:37.440
You must live well, Changning.

10:38.600 --> 10:39.730
Don't let the beasts

10:41.360 --> 10:42.670
break us again.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.150
This is the first time

10:59.150 --> 11:00.030
our school has received

11:00.030 --> 11:01.360
a large donation

11:01.360 --> 11:02.380
from society.

11:02.510 --> 11:03.320
Secretary Yu

11:03.320 --> 11:04.960
and the rest of us all
take this very seriously.

11:04.960 --> 11:05.760
Director Lin,

11:06.150 --> 11:07.480
please come up with a set of

11:07.480 --> 11:09.770
selection rules for the scholarship
as soon as possible.

11:09.770 --> 11:11.200
After all, Oceanvision International

11:11.200 --> 11:12.390
proposed to favor your

11:12.390 --> 11:14.390
Department of Atmospheric
and Oceanic Sciences.

11:14.390 --> 11:15.050
No problem.

11:15.760 --> 11:17.220
Ms. Yan from our department

11:17.220 --> 11:19.680
is already a member
of the review committee.

11:19.930 --> 11:22.410
I will draft a plan with her
as soon as possible

11:22.410 --> 11:24.010
and then submit it to the college

11:24.010 --> 11:26.030
and the review committee
for feedback and guidance.

11:26.030 --> 11:26.850
Secretary Yu,

11:27.030 --> 11:27.890
President Sun.

11:28.360 --> 11:30.630
I feel my ability and qualifications

11:30.880 --> 11:33.490
are far behind
the other committee members.

11:33.770 --> 11:36.420
So I won't be participating in

11:36.800 --> 11:38.220
the scholarship review this time.

11:38.220 --> 11:38.860
Ms. Yan.

11:39.680 --> 11:42.500
Mr. Ding from Oceanvision International
specifically requested you,

11:42.500 --> 11:44.760
which means he thinks you are qualified.

11:45.360 --> 11:48.290
Many senior professors here
are more qualified than me.

11:48.290 --> 11:49.750
I'm still just a lecturer.

11:50.070 --> 11:51.670
It's really inappropriate.

11:52.130 --> 11:52.800
Ms. Yan,

11:53.000 --> 11:54.770
are you asking for a promotion?

11:56.150 --> 11:58.080
Director Lin should have told you.

11:58.410 --> 11:59.100
This year,

11:59.200 --> 12:00.720
the matter with Li Changning

12:00.720 --> 12:01.980
has affected you.

12:02.120 --> 12:03.110
For next year's professional title review,

12:03.110 --> 12:05.170
we'll make sure to give you priority.

12:05.430 --> 12:06.070
No, no, no.

12:06.090 --> 12:07.410
That's really not what I meant.

12:07.410 --> 12:09.610
I genuinely feel I'm not qualified yet.

12:09.930 --> 12:10.600
Leaders,

12:11.050 --> 12:12.120
after the meeting,

12:12.140 --> 12:15.140
-I'll talk to Ms. Yan...
-Thank you for your generous support,

12:15.140 --> 12:16.600
but I really can't serve as

12:17.450 --> 12:19.380
a member of this review committee.

12:21.360 --> 12:22.090
In that case,

12:22.470 --> 12:23.870
we won't force it.

12:24.130 --> 12:26.530
We will respect Ms. Yan's personal wishes.

12:28.310 --> 12:29.370
Let's call it a day.

13:04.130 --> 13:04.860
You're back.

13:05.640 --> 13:06.760
Hurry up and wash your hands.

13:06.760 --> 13:07.690
Get ready to eat.

13:10.720 --> 13:11.180
Not bad.

13:17.680 --> 13:18.730
Dr. Luo?

13:19.590 --> 13:20.190
Ms. Yan.

13:20.850 --> 13:22.010
Why are you here?

13:23.660 --> 13:25.450
Cola threw up several times.

13:25.470 --> 13:27.130
You didn't answer your phone,

13:27.190 --> 13:28.710
so I called Dr. Luo.

13:28.960 --> 13:30.680
He sounded worried on the phone,

13:30.680 --> 13:32.670
so I rushed over without telling you.

13:32.670 --> 13:33.000
Well,

13:33.300 --> 13:35.010
is Cola okay now?

13:35.160 --> 13:36.160
Dr. Luo said

13:36.160 --> 13:37.370
it just ate too much.

13:38.760 --> 13:40.620
Jiale just spoiled Cola too much.

13:41.100 --> 13:42.830
I discussed it with Jiale today

13:43.090 --> 13:43.520
to see if we could

13:43.520 --> 13:44.610
let him raise

13:44.610 --> 13:45.540
Cola from now on.

13:46.560 --> 13:47.330
Can I?

13:50.450 --> 13:51.330
How about this?

13:52.740 --> 13:54.080
I'll pay you.

13:54.300 --> 13:55.490
Jiale told me

13:55.760 --> 13:58.020
this kind of hamster is quite expensive.

13:59.190 --> 14:00.680
It's indeed quite expensive.

14:00.680 --> 14:02.340
One is about over 50,000 yuan.

14:02.880 --> 14:03.850
That expensive?

14:07.800 --> 14:09.160
You two are indeed mother and son.

14:09.160 --> 14:11.820
Your shocked expressions
are exactly the same.

14:12.160 --> 14:12.800
Ms. Yan,

14:13.370 --> 14:15.280
I've already come to cook at your house.

14:15.280 --> 14:17.410
Could you not treat me like a stranger?

14:19.520 --> 14:20.250
Then go on

14:20.250 --> 14:21.280
and thank Dr. Luo.

14:21.850 --> 14:22.910
Thank you, Dr. Luo.

14:22.920 --> 14:23.850
You're welcome.

14:24.680 --> 14:26.850
I'll put the tableware and stuff

14:26.880 --> 14:27.880
over there first.

14:28.160 --> 14:28.880
Thanks.

14:32.920 --> 14:33.520
Ms. Yan.

14:33.760 --> 14:34.880
There's only one dish left to finish.

14:34.880 --> 14:35.550
I'll be quick.

14:35.550 --> 14:36.610
Just wait a moment.

14:37.040 --> 14:38.240
I'm really sorry.

14:38.370 --> 14:40.920
I should be treating you to a meal,

14:41.370 --> 14:43.300
but now you're here cooking for me.

14:43.370 --> 14:44.490
It's the least I could do.

14:44.490 --> 14:44.820
Here.

14:45.680 --> 14:48.260
After all, Jiale has been taking care of
my Cola for so long.

14:48.260 --> 14:49.400
It's just a meal.

14:50.690 --> 14:51.560
He told me

14:52.130 --> 14:53.040
he really craves

14:53.040 --> 14:54.400
his godmother's home-cooked meals,

14:54.400 --> 14:57.330
and he hasn't had a proper meal
at home for a long time.

15:01.160 --> 15:02.490
The garlic is...

15:02.950 --> 15:03.820
It's in the fridge, right?

15:03.820 --> 15:04.730
Yes, I'll get it.

15:04.730 --> 15:05.330
It's okay.

15:07.110 --> 15:07.850
Here it is.

15:09.300 --> 15:10.160
Is this enough?

15:16.610 --> 15:17.670
Are you using this?

15:18.920 --> 15:20.560
I get tinnitus sometimes.

15:21.470 --> 15:22.470
It's an old issue.

15:23.250 --> 15:24.560
If it's not organic,

15:24.680 --> 15:27.090
this condition is most likely
related to stress.

15:27.090 --> 15:27.850
If you have the time,

15:27.850 --> 15:29.310
you should go see a doctor.

15:44.010 --> 15:45.870
Is there anything I can help with?

15:46.680 --> 15:48.340
Right. There's one more dish.

15:51.560 --> 15:52.730
Sweet and sour spare ribs.

15:52.730 --> 15:54.590
Jiale said he really craves this.

16:25.530 --> 16:26.400
Thank you.

16:27.160 --> 16:28.640
You are a very good cook.

16:29.300 --> 16:30.050
Am I?

16:31.640 --> 16:33.530
And what's especially coincidental is that

16:33.530 --> 16:34.400
Leilei

16:34.890 --> 16:37.630
used to always add dried plums

16:38.400 --> 16:39.880
when making this dish too.

16:41.970 --> 16:44.170
Actually, it was Jiale who told me that.

16:44.760 --> 16:46.690
He said you only eat the plums in it.

16:49.500 --> 16:50.560
If you guys like it,

16:51.250 --> 16:52.310
I'll make it for you

16:52.650 --> 16:54.250
whenever I have time.

16:59.850 --> 17:01.580
I actually came to see you today

17:01.640 --> 17:03.370
to talk to you about something.

17:03.530 --> 17:04.730
But with Jiale there,

17:04.760 --> 17:06.290
it wasn't very convenient.

17:08.970 --> 17:10.170
You mentioned before

17:10.560 --> 17:11.839
that Yu Kexin

17:12.450 --> 17:14.650
also had that tattoo on her body, right?

17:16.619 --> 17:16.970
Yes.

17:18.599 --> 17:19.800
I took a closer look

17:19.800 --> 17:21.329
at the syllabus you sent me.

17:21.800 --> 17:22.839
Branding tattoos

17:22.839 --> 17:24.099
is one of the chapters.

17:24.450 --> 17:25.310
I was thinking,

17:25.579 --> 17:25.970
maybe those people

17:25.970 --> 17:28.359
make their other half get
specific patterns tattooed

17:28.359 --> 17:31.020
to show their possession and control
over them.

17:35.320 --> 17:36.760
You mean

17:38.650 --> 17:39.560
Yu Kexin

17:40.320 --> 17:42.780
might also have been a victim
from back then,

17:43.210 --> 17:44.010
but then,

17:45.170 --> 17:46.650
she chose to join them

17:47.080 --> 17:48.610
and keep deceiving others?

17:50.140 --> 17:51.120
Very likely.

17:55.360 --> 17:58.170
Actually, I planned to call you
to tell you about this,

17:58.170 --> 18:00.360
but Jiale suddenly sent me
a WeChat message,

18:00.360 --> 18:02.540
so I ended up coming to your house
to cook first.

18:02.540 --> 18:04.000
I hope this tiny bit of clue

18:04.760 --> 18:06.320
could be of some help to you—
though I'm not sure.

18:06.320 --> 18:07.720
It is. Of course it is.

18:08.730 --> 18:09.600
Thank you.

18:13.580 --> 18:15.310
You said those two words again.

18:15.910 --> 18:16.910
"Thank you."

18:22.820 --> 18:24.550
Calmly accepting others' help

18:24.930 --> 18:26.330
and learning to be loved—

18:27.120 --> 18:27.690
I think

18:28.600 --> 18:31.200
these are very important lessons
in our lives,

18:31.490 --> 18:32.050
right?

18:44.250 --> 18:45.110
Go back inside.

18:46.640 --> 18:47.700
It's getting cold.

18:53.040 --> 18:53.610
Well,

18:54.360 --> 18:56.090
be careful on your way back too.

18:56.510 --> 18:56.930
I will.

18:59.760 --> 19:00.490
I'm leaving.

19:25.080 --> 19:28.080
It's so late. Why haven't you
gone to take a shower yet?

19:28.210 --> 19:29.210
Although Dr. Luo

19:29.210 --> 19:30.740
likes to preach a little bit

19:31.320 --> 19:32.450
and opens up easily,

19:33.730 --> 19:34.010
if you

19:34.010 --> 19:36.120
really want to be with him,

19:36.140 --> 19:37.000
I won't object.

19:37.840 --> 19:39.900
What nonsense are you talking about?

19:39.900 --> 19:41.370
We are just friends.

19:42.560 --> 19:43.090
Oh right,

19:43.840 --> 19:45.280
when you couldn't reach me,

19:45.280 --> 19:46.960
why didn't you call your dad?

19:47.450 --> 19:48.450
Don't mention it.

19:48.970 --> 19:51.210
Miss Fang Fang texted me this afternoon,

19:51.210 --> 19:54.040
asking if my dad is working overtime
every day this week.

19:54.040 --> 19:55.570
That shouldn't be the case.

19:56.170 --> 19:58.800
Even if the meteorological bureau
is dealing with the flood season

19:58.800 --> 20:00.330
and operates 24 hours a day,

20:00.600 --> 20:02.730
they still rotate shifts every 3 days.

20:02.730 --> 20:05.010
There's no way he wouldn't be seen
at all every day.

20:05.010 --> 20:06.070
So what did you say?

20:06.410 --> 20:07.620
Well, I could only

20:07.840 --> 20:09.600
cover for him for now.

20:11.410 --> 20:12.360
Yan Jiale.

20:14.080 --> 20:15.000
So you've even learned

20:15.000 --> 20:16.930
to lie right to people's faces now?

20:17.690 --> 20:20.010
Godmother said this is called a white lie.

20:20.010 --> 20:20.560
Besides,

20:20.580 --> 20:22.950
my dad wouldn't do anything bad.

20:22.980 --> 20:24.150
I guess

20:24.540 --> 20:26.170
he's just busy trying to clear

20:26.170 --> 20:28.300
the new map of Last Island of Survival.

20:31.040 --> 20:31.840
You're right.

20:32.160 --> 20:33.490
I'll reflect on myself.

20:33.650 --> 20:35.450
From now on, if I handle something badly,

20:35.450 --> 20:36.650
remember to remind me

20:36.840 --> 20:37.730
how your godmother would handle it,

20:37.730 --> 20:38.410
okay?

20:43.710 --> 20:45.400
[The Art of Love—
Exploring the Mysteries of Love]

20:44.570 --> 20:45.680
This is Hajun.

20:45.530 --> 20:47.060
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

20:49.210 --> 20:51.250
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

20:57.130 --> 20:59.820
[The Art of Reading Minds in Love]

20:59.910 --> 21:01.550
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

21:02.840 --> 21:03.520
See that?

21:03.690 --> 21:05.120
This is the first change

21:05.120 --> 21:06.250
I'm bringing to you—

21:06.410 --> 21:07.870
crafting your personas.

21:06.780 --> 21:08.450
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

21:08.040 --> 21:08.560
I fe-

21:08.560 --> 21:10.010
I feel like I'm not even myself anymore.

21:10.010 --> 21:11.070
Of course it's you.

21:11.140 --> 21:12.600
This just brings out the side of you

21:12.600 --> 21:13.800
that's been hidden all along.

21:12.680 --> 21:13.870
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

21:13.940 --> 21:16.020
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

21:14.490 --> 21:14.890
Next.

21:16.930 --> 21:18.010
Everyone knows that

21:18.010 --> 21:19.730
Xuan was just a mechanic.

21:19.750 --> 21:21.320
But through our transformation,

21:21.320 --> 21:23.140
he completely became

21:23.320 --> 21:24.970
an outstanding racing driver.

21:24.040 --> 21:25.050
[Wavemaker Education] [Student Transformation Results]
[Before and After]

21:25.160 --> 21:27.000
[The Art of Love—
Exploring the Mysteries of Love]

21:27.100 --> 21:27.930
First impressions

21:27.140 --> 21:31.020
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

21:27.930 --> 21:31.070
determine whether the other party
is interested in getting to know you.

21:31.070 --> 21:32.730
[The Art of Love—
Exploring the Mysteries of Love]

21:31.410 --> 21:32.820
Whether you are a penniless nobody

21:32.820 --> 21:37.470
[Secrets to Finding a Partner]
[Love Guide]

21:33.040 --> 21:35.760
or a dominant alpha
that every woman longs for—

21:35.760 --> 21:38.040
it's all written on the persona
you present.

21:38.040 --> 21:39.490
From that first impression,

21:39.490 --> 21:42.080
they judge whether the value you display

21:42.080 --> 21:44.520
can provide them with

21:44.520 --> 21:46.120
enough financial security.

21:48.560 --> 21:50.600
Never doubt our expertise.

21:50.730 --> 21:51.490
Here,

21:52.930 --> 21:54.520
I am your god—

21:55.080 --> 21:57.010
a savior who lifts you out of

21:57.010 --> 21:58.120
the pit of pitiful insecurity

21:58.120 --> 21:59.730
and helps you get back on your feet,

21:59.730 --> 22:01.820
a magician who transforms you from

22:02.080 --> 22:04.120
being ignored into

22:04.800 --> 22:06.260
being universally loved.

22:13.170 --> 22:14.410
So far,

22:14.410 --> 22:16.190
the trial class worth 598 yuan is over.

22:16.190 --> 22:21.050
[Love Manual]

22:16.240 --> 22:19.450
I believe you've all witnessed
the magical transformation.

22:19.450 --> 22:21.210
The tuition for our subsequent classes is

22:21.210 --> 22:22.120
3,988 yuan,

22:22.560 --> 22:23.650
and that's where

22:23.890 --> 22:25.800
the real highlights begin—

22:26.040 --> 22:29.010
teaching you step by step
how to win a girl's heart

22:29.120 --> 22:29.840
and make her

22:30.280 --> 22:31.880
completely obedient to you.

22:32.970 --> 22:33.930
-Me!
-Me!

22:57.800 --> 22:59.080
Y-You startled me.

23:00.360 --> 23:01.560
Did you dye your hair?

23:03.010 --> 23:03.410
Wait,

23:03.800 --> 23:05.530
why are you here all of a sudden?

23:06.360 --> 23:07.420
It's Monday today.

23:08.490 --> 23:09.750
I took a day off in lieu.

23:10.520 --> 23:11.730
You've been quite busy, huh?

23:11.730 --> 23:13.390
I haven't seen you for a while.

23:13.600 --> 23:14.460
Yeah. I... I...

23:14.760 --> 23:16.520
I-I was just...

23:16.520 --> 23:17.250
Look,

23:17.600 --> 23:18.800
everyone has been sent out.

23:18.800 --> 23:20.650
I'm the only one staying behind.

23:21.730 --> 23:23.490
I've been busy lately,

23:23.690 --> 23:25.150
and I forgot to ask you out.

23:25.960 --> 23:28.220
So busy, yet you had time
to dye your hair?

23:29.410 --> 23:30.470
It's not like that.

23:32.280 --> 23:33.560
Well, the other day,

23:33.560 --> 23:34.080
I went

23:34.080 --> 23:35.140
to get a haircut, you know?

23:35.140 --> 23:37.750
The barber told me that

23:37.930 --> 23:38.990
my hair was too grey

23:39.080 --> 23:39.760
and didn't look good,

23:39.760 --> 23:41.080
and he said I should dye it.

23:41.080 --> 23:41.940
I-It's just...

23:42.250 --> 23:44.080
T-The color didn't turn out well.

23:44.080 --> 23:45.340
Making things up, huh?

23:45.670 --> 23:46.280
Go on then.

23:46.970 --> 23:48.120
I'm not making things up.

23:48.120 --> 23:49.780
I'll give you another chance.

23:50.450 --> 23:51.310
What happened?

23:54.560 --> 23:55.250
Well...

23:58.700 --> 23:59.890
I just over-dyed it.

24:01.890 --> 24:04.210
Students participating in
the second phase of training,

24:04.210 --> 24:05.470
I'm glad to see you all.

24:06.320 --> 24:07.320
From now on,

24:07.600 --> 24:09.490
I will turn you beginners

24:09.730 --> 24:11.490
into the best hunters.

24:12.220 --> 24:14.930
First, we use the hexagon judgment system

24:15.410 --> 24:17.360
to score and categorize your prey.

24:25.850 --> 24:27.710
The system has 2 main categories:

24:27.730 --> 24:28.250
R

24:29.040 --> 24:30.530
stands for subjective reproductive value—

24:30.530 --> 24:33.380
[Hexagon Judgment System]

24:30.760 --> 24:32.160
whether she's attractive

24:32.160 --> 24:33.890
and whether you want to sleep with her.

24:33.890 --> 24:36.360
X stands for objective inner value—

24:36.360 --> 24:37.730
whether she's a good girl

24:37.730 --> 24:39.890
and whether you'd want to marry her.

24:40.360 --> 24:41.520
Higher R value means

24:41.690 --> 24:43.040
she's suitable as a bedmate.

24:43.040 --> 24:44.410
Just hit it and quit it.

24:45.080 --> 24:48.690
Only when both R and X are high
is it worth your effort

24:49.010 --> 24:50.730
to maintain a long-term relationship
with her.

24:50.730 --> 24:52.040
But here comes the problem.

24:52.040 --> 24:55.010
Just because you want to sleep with her
doesn't mean she's easy to get.

24:55.010 --> 24:55.930
So the next step

24:55.060 --> 24:58.660
[Hexagon Judgment System]

24:55.930 --> 24:57.730
is to analyze the openness of the NPC

24:57.730 --> 25:00.280
that you want to conquer.

25:00.280 --> 25:01.280
The term is called

25:01.930 --> 25:03.040
the "promiscuity signal."

25:02.910 --> 25:03.870
[Promiscuity Signal]

25:03.560 --> 25:04.520
For different women,

25:03.930 --> 25:04.850
[Level A: Players]
[Level B: Lonely Women]

25:04.520 --> 25:06.170
as long as you use the corresponding mode

25:04.870 --> 25:06.030
[Level C: Obedient Women]
[Level D: Conservative Women]

25:06.170 --> 25:07.900
and give the prepared answers,

25:07.970 --> 25:09.560
you can get them in a minute.

25:11.170 --> 25:12.170
The "playboy mode"

25:12.170 --> 25:13.010
is used to deal with

25:13.010 --> 25:14.120
Level A, "players",

25:13.460 --> 25:14.610
[Level A: Players] [Promiscuity Signal]

25:14.120 --> 25:15.080
and Level B, "lonely women."

25:14.660 --> 25:17.180
[Emperor Mode] [Bard Mode] [Playboy Mode]

25:17.460 --> 25:18.600
The "emperor mode"

25:18.600 --> 25:20.450
is used to deal with Level C,
"obedient women",

25:19.970 --> 25:22.240
[Level C: Obedient Women]
[Promiscuity Signal]

25:20.450 --> 25:22.260
and Level D, "conservative women."

25:22.260 --> 25:26.880
[Emperor Mode] [Bard Mode] [Playboy Mode]

25:27.280 --> 25:29.650
While the "bard" is
the ultimate trump card.

25:27.340 --> 25:30.290
[Level A: Players] [Promiscuity Signal]

25:30.340 --> 25:33.650
[Wanshun Jewelry]

25:31.800 --> 25:32.250
Hello.

25:44.560 --> 25:47.840
[Level C: Obedient Women]
[Promiscuity Signal]

25:47.860 --> 25:49.050
[Emperor Mode] [Bard Mode] [Playboy Mode]

25:49.210 --> 25:52.420
[Emperor Mode]

25:51.170 --> 25:51.560
Hi.

25:59.120 --> 26:01.760
[Emperor Traits]

25:59.930 --> 26:00.370
Hi.

26:00.600 --> 26:01.860
Hello.

26:01.910 --> 26:04.240
[Obedient Woman Traits] [Prey Info]

26:02.250 --> 26:03.110
Obedient women

26:03.360 --> 26:04.650
are usually pure and kind,

26:04.350 --> 26:11.550
[Emperor Mode] [Emperor Traits]

26:05.080 --> 26:06.730
and they're easy to trust others.

26:06.730 --> 26:07.730
To deal with them,

26:08.360 --> 26:10.280
you need to appear mature and steady.

26:10.280 --> 26:11.010
Suddenly meeting you here...

26:11.010 --> 26:12.600
At the same time,
you need to show the dominance of a boss

26:11.670 --> 26:18.960
[Prey Info] [Obedient Woman Traits]

26:13.120 --> 26:14.410
to establish their worship of you.

26:14.410 --> 26:15.410
Can I get your contact info?

26:15.410 --> 26:17.070
These girls are easy targets.

26:17.520 --> 26:19.410
One of our students even managed to
get into a girl's pants

26:19.020 --> 26:21.640
[Emperor Mode] [Emperor Traits]

26:19.410 --> 26:21.730
-the third day after they met.
-I wouldn't usually be so abrupt,

26:21.680 --> 26:24.570
[Prey Info] [Obedient Woman Traits]

26:22.210 --> 26:23.810
but from the moment I saw you,

26:24.660 --> 26:28.190
[Emperor Mode] [Emperor Traits]

26:25.120 --> 26:25.890
I knew

26:25.970 --> 26:27.300
that if I let you slip by,

26:27.840 --> 26:29.300
I'd definitely regret it.

26:29.650 --> 26:30.510
Scan my QR code.

26:30.970 --> 26:31.410
Okay.

26:31.600 --> 26:35.780
[Mission Accomplished]

26:36.570 --> 26:37.230
[The Cutest in the World]
[Decline] [Answer]

26:46.800 --> 26:47.470
Well...

26:47.690 --> 26:48.970
I-I'm outside.

26:49.890 --> 26:50.890
Outside where?

26:51.320 --> 26:53.600
And I asked what you were doing.

26:54.320 --> 26:54.690
I...

26:55.040 --> 26:56.760
I'm just at the pedestrian street.

26:56.760 --> 26:58.890
I'm here to buy a few things with Jiale.

26:59.320 --> 27:01.650
You're shopping?
Why didn't you ask me to come along?

27:01.650 --> 27:02.410
Well...

27:03.120 --> 27:03.720
It's fine.

27:04.320 --> 27:06.520
You guys haven't had dinner yet, have you?

27:06.520 --> 27:08.280
How about I come find you now?

27:08.450 --> 27:09.080
No, no, no.

27:09.450 --> 27:10.170
Don't come over.

27:10.170 --> 27:12.210
W-We'll go back as soon as we finish.

27:14.010 --> 27:14.840
Lu Yifeng.

27:17.080 --> 27:18.520
I'll give you one last chance.

27:18.520 --> 27:19.690
Tell me the truth.

27:19.690 --> 27:21.220
What exactly are you doing?

27:21.800 --> 27:24.120
You know I hate men who lie the most.

27:24.450 --> 27:25.490
No, I'm not lying.

27:26.080 --> 27:26.800
I trust you

27:26.800 --> 27:27.490
and like you

27:27.490 --> 27:29.410
because I feel you're different from them.

27:29.410 --> 27:30.410
I'm really not lying to you.

27:30.410 --> 27:31.540
Alright, Lu Yifeng.

27:31.560 --> 27:32.800
You're not only insulting my feelings,

27:32.800 --> 27:34.260
but also my intelligence!

27:34.410 --> 27:34.800
I...

27:36.600 --> 27:37.120
Hello?

27:40.490 --> 27:42.290
I think your intuition is right.

27:43.450 --> 27:45.510
You're definitely being cheated on.

27:48.410 --> 27:49.010
Next,

27:49.450 --> 27:52.170
let's start learning the core technique
of a manipulator:

27:52.170 --> 27:53.640
the Five-Step Trap Method.

27:53.640 --> 27:56.050
[Five-Step Trap—
Pit No.1: Curiosity Trap]

27:53.890 --> 27:56.040
Pit No. 1, the Curiosity Trap,

27:56.280 --> 27:58.250
is about using a certain sense of mystery

27:58.250 --> 28:00.720
to arouse your prey's curiosity
and desire to explore you

28:00.720 --> 28:05.180
[Five-Step Trap—
Pit No.1: Curiosity Trap]

28:01.040 --> 28:02.410
As for what kind of woman

28:02.410 --> 28:05.010
is curious about what kind of man,

28:05.320 --> 28:07.180
you need to base it on her category

28:07.690 --> 28:09.690
and tailor it specifically for her.

28:09.900 --> 28:12.100
For example, with an obedient woman...

28:12.280 --> 28:13.280
How have you been?

28:13.450 --> 28:14.040
I dreamed of you again.

28:14.040 --> 28:15.600
You need to use sweet words

28:15.730 --> 28:17.170
to show your gentleness.

28:17.280 --> 28:19.210
Can you give me a chance to explain?

28:19.520 --> 28:20.520
I miss you so much.

28:20.970 --> 28:22.300
Please don't ignore me.

28:23.600 --> 28:24.350
Changning.

28:25.010 --> 28:25.810
Are you there?

28:25.980 --> 28:33.910
[Message sent but rejected
by the recipient]

28:31.730 --> 28:32.530
Are you crazy?

28:32.560 --> 28:34.040
For instance, with a player,

28:34.040 --> 28:35.410
you need to lower yourself

28:35.410 --> 28:37.650
and show your helplessness and innocence.

28:36.350 --> 28:39.170
[Fitness Center]

28:37.650 --> 28:38.600
What are you doing here?

28:38.600 --> 28:40.490
I must explain that matter to you.

28:40.650 --> 28:41.370
I'm not interested.

28:41.370 --> 28:41.960
[Fitness Center]

28:41.840 --> 28:43.970
I know in your heart, I've always been...

28:43.970 --> 28:46.180
I only have 30 minutes to exercise a day.

28:46.320 --> 28:47.010
Later at 6:30,

28:47.010 --> 28:48.800
I have a Zoom meeting with the US team.

28:48.800 --> 28:51.000
I have no time to listen to your romance.

28:55.890 --> 28:57.080
You might think

28:58.280 --> 28:59.890
writing letters is childish.

28:59.890 --> 29:02.290
You might even laugh at me
after reading it.

29:02.650 --> 29:06.180
But I still wanted to write a letter
to you to explain it clearly.

29:07.210 --> 29:08.740
If you don't want to read it,

29:09.650 --> 29:10.800
just throw it away.

29:24.690 --> 29:26.730
The keyword for Pit No.2, Obsession Trap,

29:26.730 --> 29:27.590
is subversion.

29:28.170 --> 29:30.120
Show your hidden side.

29:30.350 --> 29:33.000
[The Only Person Who Sees
Your Hidden Traits]

29:30.490 --> 29:33.400
Show your hidden fragility,

29:33.450 --> 29:34.520
your distress,

29:34.520 --> 29:35.560
and your vulnerability.

29:35.560 --> 29:38.360
Arouse their sympathy for you

29:38.360 --> 29:40.360
and their inner maternal instinct.

29:41.560 --> 29:43.080
Are the stories in your letter

29:43.080 --> 29:43.800
all true?

29:49.080 --> 29:49.730
It happened right where

29:49.730 --> 29:51.210
I took you to that day.

29:52.650 --> 29:53.800
So,

29:54.280 --> 29:56.680
you knew she broke up with
her ex-boyfriend

29:57.120 --> 29:59.040
and tried to jump off the bridge in pain.

29:59.040 --> 30:00.440
Not only did you save her,

30:00.800 --> 30:03.000
but you also insisted on being with her.

30:04.410 --> 30:05.010
Well,

30:05.650 --> 30:07.840
shouldn't we comfort and support

30:08.280 --> 30:09.280
someone who is sad and upset

30:09.280 --> 30:10.210
when we see them?

30:12.170 --> 30:15.430
Isn't that taking advantage of
someone's vulnerability?

30:15.650 --> 30:17.110
Call it whatever you want.

30:18.040 --> 30:20.300
I just didn't want to see her
in such pain.

30:20.930 --> 30:22.730
You must make the prey think

30:23.560 --> 30:24.020
that she

30:24.410 --> 30:28.170
is the only one who sees

30:28.520 --> 30:29.650
your hidden traits.

30:42.560 --> 30:43.890
So she stabbed you here?

30:46.600 --> 30:48.280
You said when she stabbed you,

30:48.840 --> 30:51.370
she even called out
her ex-boyfriend's name?

30:56.010 --> 30:58.010
I know you all think I'm ridiculous,

30:58.210 --> 30:59.360
even pitiful.

31:00.210 --> 31:01.340
But I don't think so.

31:02.120 --> 31:04.320
She just got out of the mental hospital.

31:04.840 --> 31:06.360
I believe stabbing me
wasn't her intention.

31:06.360 --> 31:09.220
She just mistook me for someone else
at that moment.

31:09.590 --> 31:11.650
But she was so sick and in so much pain,

31:12.280 --> 31:14.480
and you guys only mock and belittle her.

31:16.240 --> 31:16.890
Why?

31:31.730 --> 31:33.330
Look at my poor little thing,

31:34.600 --> 31:35.760
still heartbroken.

32:04.080 --> 32:04.970
So many dishes?

32:05.730 --> 32:06.320
Jiale,

32:07.210 --> 32:08.740
you troubled Dr. Luo again.

32:09.320 --> 32:10.170
What Dr. Luo?

32:10.890 --> 32:12.650
Mom, why are you here?

32:13.450 --> 32:15.580
Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

32:15.690 --> 32:16.760
I didn't need you to pick me up,

32:16.760 --> 32:17.760
so why should I tell you

32:17.760 --> 32:18.890
and waste your time?

32:19.360 --> 32:20.600
Jiale, what are you doing?

32:20.600 --> 32:21.490
Did you wash your hands?

32:21.490 --> 32:22.890
Go on, go wash your hands.

32:22.970 --> 32:23.900
Wash them clean.

32:24.320 --> 32:25.490
Keeping a mouse at home,

32:25.490 --> 32:26.210
so dirty.

32:26.210 --> 32:27.490
It's a hamster.

32:27.490 --> 32:27.930
Jiale,

32:28.010 --> 32:29.080
listen to your grandmother.

32:29.080 --> 32:29.810
Go wash them.

32:47.010 --> 32:47.840
Uncle Ding

32:47.840 --> 32:49.600
did our family such a big favor.

32:49.800 --> 32:51.760
We should go thank him in person.

32:52.410 --> 32:54.010
I know you are thin-skinned.

32:54.080 --> 32:55.080
Tomorrow happens to be the weekend—

32:55.080 --> 32:56.220
I'll go with you.

32:56.450 --> 32:57.450
He's so sick,

32:57.800 --> 32:58.490
I should also

32:58.490 --> 32:59.680
go visit him more,

32:59.800 --> 33:01.530
so he won't feel disheartened.

33:04.850 --> 33:05.420
Jiale,

33:06.730 --> 33:08.170
go do your homework.

33:17.800 --> 33:18.320
Mom,

33:19.450 --> 33:20.970
I already told the school

33:22.040 --> 33:22.650
that I

33:23.120 --> 33:25.180
couldn't be on the review committee.

33:25.890 --> 33:26.490
Why?

33:30.450 --> 33:31.560
I think

33:33.410 --> 33:34.800
I'm not qualified enough.

33:34.800 --> 33:36.260
How are you not qualified?

33:37.170 --> 33:38.030
Over the years,

33:38.210 --> 33:39.840
have you written fewer papers than others

33:39.840 --> 33:41.280
or not taken your teaching seriously?

33:41.280 --> 33:43.800
I felt it was unfair that
you didn't get promoted this year.

33:43.800 --> 33:46.040
Now you have no power, no influence,
and no husband,

33:46.040 --> 33:48.570
so of course anyone dares to
step all over you.

33:49.490 --> 33:51.550
Mom, stop making things worse for me.

33:51.730 --> 33:52.870
I've told you

33:53.280 --> 33:55.580
not to worry about my work.

33:56.040 --> 33:57.360
I don't want you or anyone else

33:57.360 --> 33:58.820
getting involved in this.

34:01.320 --> 34:02.920
How am I making things worse?

34:03.360 --> 34:04.650
At my age,

34:04.650 --> 34:06.080
lowering myself to plead with someone—

34:06.080 --> 34:07.480
who do you think it's for?

34:07.800 --> 34:10.409
Does clinging to that intellectual pride
of yours help at all?

34:10.409 --> 34:12.239
When Jiale needs money for school,

34:12.239 --> 34:13.489
for extracurricular classes,

34:13.489 --> 34:15.010
or for medical bills,

34:15.010 --> 34:17.070
then you'll know what's good for you.

34:18.810 --> 34:20.010
Mom, I'm begging you.

34:21.330 --> 34:24.190
I really don't want to owe anyone
any favor anymore.

34:24.850 --> 34:26.510
Do you think I want to owe them?

34:27.600 --> 34:30.460
Whose fault is it
that our lives turned out this way?

34:31.560 --> 34:33.360
Don't I want to hold my head high?

34:34.449 --> 34:35.980
When your father was alive,

34:36.199 --> 34:37.600
everyone looked up to us.

34:39.120 --> 34:40.580
Being a widow with a child—

34:41.199 --> 34:42.530
do you think it was easy?

34:44.040 --> 34:45.040
After your dad passed away,

34:45.040 --> 34:46.840
you only thought about leaving.

34:47.370 --> 34:48.639
You never liked calling,

34:48.639 --> 34:50.719
and you didn't come home for the holidays.

34:50.719 --> 34:51.440
Fine.

34:52.159 --> 34:53.080
Don't rely on anyone

34:53.080 --> 34:53.880
or owe anyone.

34:53.969 --> 34:55.500
Just consider me dead, too!

34:56.080 --> 34:56.639
Mom,

34:57.600 --> 34:58.720
please don't be mad.

34:58.720 --> 35:00.050
That's not what I meant.

35:00.810 --> 35:03.140
I‘ll never meddle in your business again.

35:04.850 --> 35:06.510
And don't call me Mom anymore.

35:07.560 --> 35:08.120
Mom.

35:09.770 --> 35:10.160
Mo-

35:28.160 --> 35:28.640
Mom,

35:29.330 --> 35:30.930
please don't be mad, okay?

35:30.930 --> 35:31.930
It's all my fault.

35:36.450 --> 35:37.450
When you get home,

35:37.770 --> 35:39.500
can you send me a WeChat message

35:39.640 --> 35:40.840
so I know you're safe?

36:03.890 --> 36:06.020
Grandma brought this here yesterday.

36:07.560 --> 36:08.560
Did she reply?

36:09.310 --> 36:10.440
Has she gotten home?

36:12.010 --> 36:13.040
She should have.

36:17.520 --> 36:18.450
Is that Grandma?

36:19.240 --> 36:20.100
It's my boss,

36:22.040 --> 36:22.890
Director Lin.

36:23.330 --> 36:24.260
Hello, Yan Ling.

36:24.410 --> 36:25.420
It's urgent,

36:25.450 --> 36:27.310
so I'll get straight to the point.

36:27.450 --> 36:29.210
Are you close to that Mr. Ding

36:29.230 --> 36:31.160
from Oceanvision International?

36:32.290 --> 36:33.330
Kind of, I guess.

36:34.610 --> 36:36.420
He used to work for my dad.

36:36.720 --> 36:38.010
So you are close.

36:39.450 --> 36:40.640
Here's the situation.

36:40.640 --> 36:41.450
President Sun

36:41.470 --> 36:43.040
just had a meeting with them.

36:43.040 --> 36:44.120
Since your name wasn't on

36:44.120 --> 36:46.160
the list the review committee
submitted to them,

36:46.160 --> 36:47.340
they suddenly changed their mind

36:47.340 --> 36:49.400
and said they'd cancel the donation.

36:49.850 --> 36:50.620
Is that so?

36:51.040 --> 36:52.970
That's over 10 million in real cash—

36:52.970 --> 36:54.190
it's not a small sum.

36:54.490 --> 36:55.720
After President Sun came back,

36:55.720 --> 36:57.850
he called a meeting
with the relevant staff.

36:57.850 --> 36:59.660
In the end, everyone agreed

36:59.930 --> 37:00.640
that

37:00.640 --> 37:02.440
you should represent our school

37:02.810 --> 37:04.330
and go talk to Mr. Ding,

37:04.330 --> 37:05.240
to see why they

37:05.240 --> 37:06.500
decided not to donate.

37:07.850 --> 37:08.290
Hello?

37:09.080 --> 37:10.880
Ms. Yan, are you listening to me?

37:11.520 --> 37:12.380
I'm listening.

37:13.560 --> 37:14.560
Looking at it now,

37:14.770 --> 37:15.290
Mr. Ding's choice

37:15.290 --> 37:16.290
of our school,

37:16.340 --> 37:17.410
especially our department,

37:17.410 --> 37:18.820
had a lot to do with

37:19.080 --> 37:20.040
you being here.

37:20.680 --> 37:21.250
So,

37:21.520 --> 37:22.570
the school and I

37:22.720 --> 37:24.920
hope you can put aside personal grudges

37:24.930 --> 37:26.880
and think more about
the school and the students.

37:26.880 --> 37:29.330
I don't have any grudges
against our school.

37:29.330 --> 37:29.970
All the better

37:29.970 --> 37:31.410
then.

37:31.440 --> 37:33.240
Please go have a proper talk with him

37:33.240 --> 37:34.560
and try to persuade him.

37:34.560 --> 37:35.490
This scholarship

37:35.490 --> 37:38.370
will prioritize
students with financial difficulties.

37:38.370 --> 37:39.080
Yan Ling,

37:39.080 --> 37:41.320
make sure to convey our sincerity

37:41.640 --> 37:44.700
and do a good job persuading him
on behalf of the school.

37:45.850 --> 37:47.380
No. 3 of the Five-Step Trap:

37:47.450 --> 37:49.640
Pit No. 3, the Lure Trap.

37:49.970 --> 37:52.850
When you've successfully attracted
your prey

37:52.850 --> 37:54.720
with Curiosity Trap and Obsession Trap,

37:54.720 --> 37:55.330
it's time

37:55.330 --> 37:58.080
to lead her into Pit No. 3, the Lure Trap.

37:58.160 --> 38:01.440
A skilled hunter doesn't actively
chase the prey,

38:01.680 --> 38:04.720
but makes the prey actively
follow your demands,

38:04.720 --> 38:05.850
follow your rhythm,

38:05.850 --> 38:07.520
and obey your words, until...

38:09.720 --> 38:12.050
They fall right into the trap themselves.

38:12.320 --> 38:14.980
I ordered your favorite
home-style braised yellow croaker.

38:14.980 --> 38:16.040
I didn't ask you out

38:17.010 --> 38:18.330
to eat.

38:18.330 --> 38:19.490
The yellow croaker here

38:19.490 --> 38:20.620
is all wild-caught.

38:20.720 --> 38:22.410
When I heard you wanted to see me,

38:22.410 --> 38:25.080
-I thought this place is the most suitable...
-I've said

38:25.080 --> 38:25.940
I'm not eating.

38:28.370 --> 38:29.680
Do your words count?

38:30.850 --> 38:31.520
You asked me

38:32.010 --> 38:33.640
to stay out of your life

38:33.640 --> 38:34.650
and not bother you anymore.

38:34.650 --> 38:35.930
I did it.

38:36.680 --> 38:38.120
But you are still not happy.

38:38.120 --> 38:40.380
You canceled the scholarship on purpose

38:41.230 --> 38:42.960
just to make me come and beg you.

38:45.450 --> 38:47.580
I never expected you'd see me this way.

38:48.330 --> 38:48.890
Ling,

38:49.760 --> 38:51.850
how did we end up like this?

38:57.160 --> 38:58.550
Actually, this restaurant

38:58.550 --> 39:01.480
is most famous for its
osmanthus chestnut ice cream.

39:02.290 --> 39:04.090
But I know you don't eat dessert.

39:06.640 --> 39:09.240
You see, I keep everything about you
in my mind.

39:10.770 --> 39:12.500
You're supposed to do the same.

39:13.080 --> 39:16.140
It was me who stayed with you
through the hardest times.

39:17.520 --> 39:19.120
We will always be

39:20.240 --> 39:22.100
the closest people in this world.

39:28.240 --> 39:29.900
Fish maw and old chicken soup.

39:30.640 --> 39:31.970
It's full of collagen.

39:32.890 --> 39:34.420
It's the best for you girls.

39:34.680 --> 39:36.280
Here, eat it while it's warm.

39:40.680 --> 39:41.200
What,

39:41.640 --> 39:42.290
do you want me

39:42.290 --> 39:45.020
to coax you into eating
like when you were little?

39:47.970 --> 39:49.230
Come on, be a good girl.

39:50.160 --> 39:51.120
You need to eat well.

39:51.120 --> 39:53.240
Only after you've eaten enough
can you grow strong,

39:53.240 --> 39:54.190
and then...

39:59.720 --> 40:00.780
Is this necessary?

40:01.840 --> 40:03.470
It's just a meal.

40:03.930 --> 40:05.990
As if I'm going to do something to you.

40:06.970 --> 40:08.040
Your mom carried bags of stuff

40:08.040 --> 40:09.500
to visit me in the hospital

40:09.530 --> 40:11.530
and beg me to help you no matter what.

40:11.720 --> 40:13.980
And you're the one who asked me out today.

40:14.240 --> 40:15.810
Just give me a straight answer.

40:15.810 --> 40:18.340
Do you want me to donate
that 10 million or not?

40:20.490 --> 40:21.640
It's the school that wants it.

40:21.640 --> 40:23.300
I don't care about the school.

40:23.370 --> 40:25.260
If you say it, I'll donate.

40:31.060 --> 40:32.330
Say it.

40:35.490 --> 40:37.220
Say that it's you who want this,

40:38.520 --> 40:40.050
that it's what you wish for.

41:02.040 --> 41:02.890
Say it.

41:03.890 --> 41:06.170
Say that it's you who want you to do this,

41:06.970 --> 41:08.500
that it's what you wish for.

41:08.750 --> 41:09.260
This...

41:09.520 --> 41:10.440
It's me who

41:10.680 --> 41:12.120
want you to do this.

41:14.850 --> 41:16.560
This is what I wish for.

41:20.100 --> 41:24.850
[The Dark Romance]

41:30.930 --> 41:31.630
Let me do it, sister-in-law.

41:31.630 --> 41:32.060
Let me.

41:33.120 --> 41:34.320
Sorry to trouble you.

41:35.680 --> 41:36.010
Here.

41:39.240 --> 41:40.560
Please take good care of Ling.

41:40.560 --> 41:41.360
Get in the car.

41:45.450 --> 41:45.910
Come on.

41:47.080 --> 41:48.140
Go ahead and get in.

41:48.410 --> 41:49.160
Listen to your uncle.
